@startuml
title Job Lifecycle — State Machine

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #666
  ArrowColor #444
  FontSize 13
}
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam noteBorderColor #CCBB44

[*] --> PENDING : Agency creates job\n(INSTALLATION / MAINTENANCE\n/ REMOVAL / INSPECTION)

PENDING --> PENDING : Agency unassigns\nTradePerson

PENDING --> ACCEPTED : TradePerson\naccepts job

PENDING --> CANCELLED : Agency cancels

ACCEPTED --> ACCEPTED : TradePerson assigns /\nreassigns ServiceStaff

ACCEPTED --> IN_PROGRESS : ServiceStaff\nstarts on-site work

ACCEPTED --> NOE_SCHEDULED : Agency schedules\n"Notice of Entry" date

ACCEPTED --> PENDING : TradePerson unassigns\n(returns to pool)

NOE_SCHEDULED --> ACCEPTED : Tenant rejects NOE\nor date changes

NOE_SCHEDULED --> IN_PROGRESS : NOE accepted,\nwork begins

IN_PROGRESS --> COMPLETED : ServiceStaff\nmarks complete

IN_PROGRESS --> CANCELLED : Agency cancels\n(with reason)

COMPLETED --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

note right of PENDING
  Notification: TradePerson
  receives email + push +
  optional SMS with
  accept_job_link
end note

note right of ACCEPTED
  ServiceStaff auto-assigned
  and auto-accepts if they
  create own Maintenance job
end note

note right of COMPLETED
  If INSTALLATION job:
  alarm goes live on property
end note

@enduml
